          a(xmlns:cc="http://creativecommons.org/ns#", href="http://www.tripadvisor.com", property="cc:attributionName", rel="cc:attributionURL") TripAdvisor, LLC
          |  is licensed under a 
          a(rel="license", href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/deed.en_US") Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported License
          | .

  script(type='application/javascript', src='/underscore-min.js')
  script(type='application/javascript', src='//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.min.js')
